lu_part1: Wann s du miss nomaachen, wat dee kann,
lu_part2: da miss de de Plakege weisen.
en_literal_translation_p1: If you have to imitate what he can do,
en_literal_translation_p2: then you must show the policemen.
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p1: If you can't do it better,
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p2: don't try to compete with the best.
